OL,3,CMurderer jailed for 'senseless'
OL,4,Ckilling of elderly man in his own home
OL,6,FA murderer has been jailed after
OL,7,Fcarrying out a "senseless and violent"
OL,8,Fattack on a 72-year-old man in his own
OL,9,Fhome.
OL,11,FJason Holdgate, 32, of no fixed
OL,12,Faddress, was sentenced at Leeds Crown
OL,13,FCourt on Friday, having "preyed on"
OL,14,FMichael Bradley before killing him in
OL,15,FYork last year.
OL,17,FPolice discovered Mr Bradley with
OL,18,Fserious injuries, including a stab
OL,19,Fwound to the neck, in his home on
OL,20,FWhitethorn Close on 4 November 2024.
