OL,3,CMurderer jailed for 'senseless'
OL,4,Ckilling of elderly man in his own home
OL,6,FOfficers say they had been called by
OL,7,Fworried neighbours who had not seen
OL,8,Fhim for several days. He was declared
OL,9,Fdead at the scene by paramedics.
OL,11,FEnquiries revealed Holdgate had been
OL,12,Fstaying at Mr Bradley's home in the
OL,13,Ftwo weeks before the incident, along
OL,14,Fwith Nicola Anne Beck, 42, also of no
OL,15,Ffixed address, according to North
OL,16,FYorkshire Police.
OL,18,FThe pair, who were both drug users,
OL,19,Fhad reportedly befriended Mr Bradley,
OL,20,Fwho allowed them to stay at his house
OL,21,Fand use his car.
