OL,3,CMurderer jailed for 'senseless'
OL,4,Ckilling of elderly man in his own home
OL,6,FHoldgate and Beck were both charged
OL,7,Fwith the theft of Mr Bradley's car
OL,8,Fafter selling it to a member of the
OL,9,Fpublic.
OL,11,FDetective Superintendent Fran
OL,12,FNaughton, head of Major and Organised
OL,13,FCrime at North Yorkshire Police, said:
OL,14,F"Holdgate and Beck preyed on Mr
OL,15,FBradley and took advantage of him out
OL,16,Fof greed. Tragically, that cost him
OL,17,Fhis life in the most senseless and
OL,18,Fviolent way."
