OL,3,CMurderer jailed for 'senseless'
OL,4,Ckilling of elderly man in his own home
OL,6,FMs Naughton added: "We may never know
OL,7,Fthe motive for his murder, but we do
OL,8,Fknow that Holdgate carried out a
OL,9,Fsustained attack, using a hammer and a
OL,10,Fknife, resulting in multiple injuries.
OL,11,FHe is now facing the consequences of
OL,12,Fhis horrific violence."
OL,14,FHoldgate, pleaded guilty to killing Mr
OL,15,FBradley on Friday 14 March.
OL,17,FHe was handed a life sentence and will
OL,18,Fserve a minimum of 18 years.
